      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>careful about \"moving forward.\" what does that even mean? it just feels like a cycle of pretending to be alive when the person who actually made me feel alive is gone. it feels like i'm just dragging this heavy, useless body around for no reason. it's exhausting. it feels more like a chore than a life.",
