    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like i'm waiting for something that's never coming back. everything is just... stagnant. i'm just tired of the struggle to find a reason to keep going when every reason feels fake. it's like i'm just stuck in this waiting room of a life. why is it so hard for people to understand that sometimes there just isn't a \"way through\" it?",
